<p><i><b>Anathem</b></i> is a 2008 <a href="/wiki/Speculative_fiction" title="Speculative fiction">speculative fiction</a> <a href="/wiki/Novel" title="Novel">novel</a> by <a href="/wiki/Neal_Stephenson" title="Neal Stephenson">Neal Stephenson</a>.</p>
